rows.label: qst002503_msg0002
rows.name:
Huh? Where is Mylak?
Not with friends?

rows.label: qst002503_msg0003
rows.name:
Oh no... Mylak get eaten by
scary monsters?!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0004
rows.name:
How tragic...
Losing partner of long time...

rows.label: qst002503_msg0005
rows.name: What shall we say about Mylak?

rows.label: qst002503_msg0006
rows.name: He was really worried about you

rows.label: qst002503_msg0007
rows.name: He might not care about you at all

rows.label: qst002503_msg0008
rows.name:
Oh... Mylak waiting for Fumufumu
very worried?

rows.label: qst002503_msg0009
rows.name:
Of course Mylak worry. Partners
never separate from silly wordfight!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0010
rows.name:
Must go back to Mylak and
show him Fumufumu safe!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0012
rows.name: Mylak is man of such cold heart?!

rows.label: qst002503_msg0013
rows.name:
Fumufumu must go back and lecture
Mylak on meaning of friendship!
